        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100">
          <Image src={ServiceTicketThumb} width={1920} alt="Service Ticket System thumbnail" class="project-thumb" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 540px, 100vw" format="avif" quality={90} />
        </div>

        <div class="project-content mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
          <p>Built a secure, 24/7 live ticketing system featuring RBAC and enterprise-grade auth.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="tech-chip">Node.js</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">JWT</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">TiDB</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">React</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">Tailwind</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">Render</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">Vercel</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-actions">
            <a href="#" class="card-action-btn">Source Code</a>
            <a href="#" class="card-action-btn">Live Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group project-card overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-black bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg" role="button" tabindex="0" onclick="if (!event.target.closest('a')) window.location.href='/projects/todo-list-app'" onkeydown="if (event.key === 'Enter') window.location.href='/projects/todo-list-app'">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-slate-500">Project</p>
            <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950">To-Do List App</h3>
          </div>
          <span class="project-tag">TypeScript</span>
        </div>

        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100">
          <Image src={TodoThumb} width={1920} alt="To-Do List App thumbnail" class="project-thumb todo-crop" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 540px, 100vw" format="avif" quality={90} />
        </div>

        <div class="project-content mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
          <p>Full-Stack Developer - Integrated a mobile-to-cloud task manager with automated CI/CD via Expo Services.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="tech-chip">React Native</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">EAS</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">TiDB</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">Render</span>
            <span class="tech-chip">Vercel</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-actions">
            <a href="#" class="card-action-btn">Source Code</a>
            <a href="#" class="card-action-btn">Live Demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="group project-card overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-black bg-white/95 p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg" role="button" tabindex="0" onclick="if (!event.target.closest('a')) window.location.href='/projects/h100-ecolodge'" onkeydown="if (event.key === 'Enter') window.location.href='/projects/h100-ecolodge'">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
